ISLAMABAD, Nov 24 (APP): A Ministerial delegation of Belarus led by Foreign Minister Maxim Ryzhenkov arrived here on Sunday ahead of the visit of the President of Belarus Aleksandr Lukashenko.
Interior Minister Mohsin Naqvi, Additional Foreign Secretary (Europe) Ambassador Shafqat Ali Khan, and Pakistan’s Ambassador to Belarus, Sajjad Haider Khan welcomed the delegation at the airport.
